-- Lockheed Will Sell Enterprise Integration Unit to Veritas for $815 Million
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2010-10-13T12:00:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/lockheed-will-sell-enterprise-integration-unit-to-veritas-for-815-million.html
Lockheed Martin Corp. announced that
it has entered into a definitive agreement to sell its
Enterprise Integration Group business to Veritas Capital for
$815 million in cash.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  